Revision history for tvpot-dl

0.7.1   Tue Mar 1 21:27:54 2011 +0900
        Fixed a bug in file name.
        Started to use HTML::Entities.

0.7.0   Tue Mar 1 20:32:46 2011 +0900
        Added --get-title and --title option.
        Added get_video_title subroutine.
        Added a test for get_video_title subroutine.

0.6.3   Sun Feb 27 18:19:19 2011 +0900
        Fixed README.

0.6.2   Sun Feb 27 17:07:12 2011 +0900
        Added POD to bin/tvpot-dl.

0.6.1   Sun Feb 27 16:27:26 2011 +0900
        Moved 02-get_video_url.t to t/.

0.6.0   Sun Feb 27 15:51:24 2011 +0900
        Removed --title option.
        Removed get_video_title subroutine.
        Started to show download progress.
        Use video ID as file name instead of video title.

0.5.0   Sun Feb 27 01:20:14 2011 +0900
        Changed some APIs.
        Added --quiet, --title and --url option.

0.4.2   Sat Feb 26 15:32:06 2011 +0900
        Added --help and --version option.

0.4.1   Thu Feb 24 09:03:34 2011 +0900
        Started to use Carp.

0.4.0   Wed Feb 23 01:44:53 2011 +0900
        Started to use movie title as file name instead of video ID.
        Added get_movie_title subroutine.
        Fixed bugs in Build.PL.

0.3.1   Tue Feb 22 23:31:57 KST 2011
        Started to use Module::Build instead of ExtUtils::MakeMaker.
        Added some tests.

0.3.0   Mon Feb 21 23:52:14 KST 2011
        Started to use Module::Starter.

0.2     Sun Feb 20 22:44:40 2011 +0900
        Support multiple arguments.
        Support URL list from STDIN.

0.1     Sun Feb 20 17:54:22 2011 +0900
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.
